productReviews.reviewText: My goldfinch loves to play with it.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 inch and weights 12 pound!
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
My terrier loves to play with it.
This Avon works outstandingly well. It beautifully improves my basketball by a lot.
